# Anti–AI-slop checks

This project uses **[vibecheck](https://github.com/yuvrajangadsingh/vibecheck)** (`@yuvrajangadsingh/vibecheck`) — static rules for common AI-generated code smells (stubs, hedging comments, risky patterns).

After substantive edits under `src/`, run:

```bash
npm run check:slop
```

Fix new findings at **error** severity before finishing. Use **warn** as signal; tune with `vibecheck --severity info` if needed.
